components.name: Validate Parameters
components.description: Validates the DAG color parameter to ensure correct environment targeting before the pipeline proceeds.

upstream_policy.description: First task in the linear pipeline.

components.name: Download Mondo OBO File
components.description: Downloads the latest Mondo OBO file from GitHub releases, checks version against S3, and uploads the file to the landing zone in S3 (skipping if uptodate).
outputs: Mondo OBO file stored in S3 (raw/landing/mondo/)

components.name: Normalize Mondo Terms
components.description: Runs a Spark job that parses the OBO file, excludes specific terms, and writes normalized ontology terms to the public Mondo terms location in S3.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after the OBO file has been successfully downloaded to S3.

components.name: Index Mondo Terms
components.description: Runs a Spark job that reads the normalized terms from S3 and indexes them into Elasticsearch using a predefined index template.
outputs: Elasticsearch index containing Mondo ontology data

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the normalization Spark job completes successfully.

components.name: Publish Mondo Dataset
components.description: Publishes the indexed Mondo dataset to downstream systems, using the version from the download step and the color parameter for environment targeting.
outputs: Published Mondo dataset (available to downstream consumers)

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful indexing of Mondo terms.

components.name: Send Slack Notification
components.description: Sends a Slack message via webhook when the pipeline completes successfully.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after all previous tasks have succeeded.
